1
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:36,200
(嚴禁入內）

2
00:01:00,637 --> 00:01:03,217
你要去哪裡？
It's got to lead somewhere.

3
00:01:07,427 --> 00:01:11,307
嗯，我們馬上就紮營，上氣不接下氣嗎？
Well, we'll stop and make camp  pretty soon. Got your breath?

4
00:01:13,307 --> 00:01:15,227
是啊，走吧
Yeah. Let's go.

5
00:01:23,907 --> 00:01:25,827
這是什麼地方？
What is this?

6
00:01:29,617 --> 00:01:34,627
以前肯定有人呆過，我們進去看看
It doesn't look like anyone's been here for  a while. Let's go inside and check it out.

7
00:01:35,127 --> 00:01:38,917
- 真的要進去嗎？ - 芭芭拉，沒事的
- Think we should?  - Barbara, who'd know the difference?

8
00:01:39,127 --> 00:01:41,127
好吧
OK.

9
00:01:46,307 --> 00:01:49,727
進來吧，沒有背包很容易過來
Besides, a little lawbreaking'll  do you good.

10
00:02:02,197 --> 00:02:04,907
你的地圖上沒有這個地方
Wonder why this place  wasn't on your map.

11
00:02:05,117 --> 00:02:07,827
可能是個秘密的地方
Maybe it's  supposed to be a secret.

12
00:02:08,037 --> 00:02:10,037
可能是
Maybe.

13
00:02:12,497 --> 00:02:14,497
嘿！
Hey!

14
00:02:16,127 --> 00:02:17,997
游泳池！
Far out!

15
00:02:31,597 --> 00:02:33,517
感覺好極了
It feels great.

16
00:02:34,097 --> 00:02:37,727
我們洗澡吧，然後好好睡個覺
Come on, let's wash off, so it won't  be so funky in that sleeping bag.

17
00:02:38,017 --> 00:02:40,527
有人會看見的
What if somebody catches us?

18
00:02:40,817 --> 00:02:43,237
有誰會看見？
Who's gonna catch us?

19
00:02:46,407 --> 00:02:48,327
這裡沒有人
There's nobody here.

20
00:02:51,327 --> 00:02:53,327
我們洗澡吧
Let's get wet.

21
00:02:54,117 --> 00:02:57,337
- 看誰先脫完 - 我從沒幹過這種事
- Last one in is a rotten egg.  - That's really original.

22
00:03:00,797 --> 00:03:02,797
- 等等 - 什麼？
- Wait a minute.  - What?

23
00:03:04,297 --> 00:03:07,507
萬一這裡是污水處理廠呢？
What if this is some kind  of a sewage treatment plant?

24
00:03:07,927 --> 00:03:09,807
白癡
Idiot.

25
00:03:12,427 --> 00:03:14,937
你又搗鬼
Now you're gonna get it.

26
00:03:18,517 --> 00:03:20,527
感覺怎麼樣？
How is it?

27
00:03:23,397 --> 00:03:25,317
我來了
Here I come.

28
00:03:32,537 --> 00:03:34,497
- 這不好笑 - 什麼？
- That's not funny.  - What?

29
00:03:34,707 --> 00:03:37,707
你咬我，不敢相信你咬我
You bit me. I can't believe  you actually bit me.

30
00:03:37,917 --> 00:03:40,707
我看起來像巫婆嗎？
What do I look like?  A creature from the black lagoon?

31
00:03:40,997 --> 00:03:44,627
你是患多疑症吧，不要開玩笑了
You are paranoid, kid. Listen,  I'll race you to the deep end.

32
00:04:05,237 --> 00:04:08,027
芭芭拉！水裡面有東西
Barbara! There's something in here!

33
00:04:08,527 --> 00:04:09,817
大衛！
David!

34
00:04:09,907 --> 00:04:11,117
他媽的！
God damn!

35
00:04:11,697 --> 00:04:13,407
大衛！
David!

36
00:04:20,997 --> 00:04:22,997
大衛?
David?

37
00:04:26,007 --> 00:04:27,927
大衛！
David!

38
00:04:30,637 --> 00:04:32,597
大衛！ 大衛！
David! David!

39
00:05:36,947 --> 00:05:41,147
《食人魚》

40
00:07:16,507 --> 00:07:19,807
- 坐吉普車去嗎？ - 我們走的是沒有鋪過的山路
- Rent a Jeep?  - She'll be on unpaved mountain roads...

41
00:07:20,007 --> 00:07:22,427
好吧，我簽字
All right. Where do I sign?

42
00:07:27,807 --> 00:07:32,317
你到了印第安泉會有吉普車在那兒等你 那邊的路非常顛簸
We're all set. At lndian Springs you'll get  a Jeep. The roads are very rough there.

43
00:07:32,737 --> 00:07:34,607
沒事
No sweat.

44
00:07:35,527 --> 00:07:37,407
- 我可以搞定的 - 我知道
- I can handle it.  - I know.

45
00:07:37,697 --> 00:07:40,117
不然的話就不派你去了
I wouldn't send you if  I didn't think you could.

46
00:07:40,407 --> 00:07:42,327
等一下，好了
Wait. Got ya.

47
00:07:45,117 --> 00:07:46,997
- 我先到印第安泉 - 對
- I found the bigamist.  - Right.

48
00:07:47,207 --> 00:07:49,497
- 那裡有吉普車在等我？ - 對
- And the bad-cheque lady?  - Right.

49
00:07:49,707 --> 00:07:53,127
- 而且路很顛簸 - 是的，那是個小鎮
- And Mo Schneider.  - Three times, but those were all in town.

50
00:07:53,417 --> 00:07:55,927
而你是在城市裡長大 而那邊是一座大山
You're a city kid.  These kids are out in the boon...

51
00:07:56,127 --> 00:07:59,217
我什麼都能找到，我的前生是一條偵探犬
I can find anything, Earl.  I'm two-thirds bloodhound.

52
00:07:59,427 --> 00:08:02,017
你僱傭我的時候我告訴過你
I told you that when you hired me.

53
00:08:05,597 --> 00:08:09,397
哦，天吶，我的票呢？我放在口袋裡了
Oh, my gosh. My ticket. I could  have sworn I put it in my pocket.

54
00:08:09,727 --> 00:08:11,607
我的票跑哪裡去了？
Where's my ticket?

55
00:08:17,817 --> 00:08:19,697
- 我完全可以搞定 - 你當然可以
- I can manage it.  - Of course you can.

56
00:08:20,027 --> 00:08:22,827
- 往銀行存錢 - 那可是我的錢
- It's money in the bank.  - My money.

57
00:08:50,397 --> 00:08:53,517
布蘭迪，你好啊
Hello, Brandy. How are you, huh?

58
00:08:59,697 --> 00:09:03,117
去一趟城裡要花我越來越多的時間了
This hike from town is  gettin' longer every week.

59
00:09:03,617 --> 00:09:07,117
- 你得弄輛車，傑克 - 我有車
- You oughta get a car, Jack.  - I got a car.

60
00:09:07,997 --> 00:09:10,627
這地方車用不了多久
It's up on blocks. That's where it belongs.

61
00:09:14,627 --> 00:09:16,627
蘇格蘭威士忌
Scotch.

62
00:09:17,627 --> 00:09:19,627
杜松子酒
Gin.

63
00:09:20,797 --> 00:09:22,717
奔農酒
Bourbon.

64
00:09:29,017 --> 00:09:30,937
還有哈奇拉酒！
Tequila!

65
00:09:32,227 --> 00:09:34,517
你真是雪中送炭啊，傑克
You're the 7th Cavalry, Jack.

66
00:09:34,727 --> 00:09:36,897
你知道我的酒正好快沒了
You know, I just ran dry today.

67
00:09:37,237 --> 00:09:40,607
那邊有燕麥片，可我不願上那裡去拿
Your corn meal is down there, but  I ain't gonna walk down and get it.

68
00:09:41,027 --> 00:09:43,527
光喝酒我可活不了
Man cannot live by booze alone.

69
00:09:47,197 --> 00:09:50,827
全都給你吧，夠了嗎？
In lieu of rent. What's up in town?

70
00:09:51,917 --> 00:09:55,417
- 鎮裡情況怎麼樣？ - 和以前一樣
- Same as usual.  - I bet you miss it, Jack, huh?

71
00:09:56,337 --> 00:10:00,717
我想你肯定想到鎮上去居住吧？ 那邊生活方便多了
I bet you miss sellin' whatever  it was. That plastic fruit.

72
00:10:01,797 --> 00:10:03,797
不
No.

73
00:10:04,427 --> 00:10:06,307
看看這河
Got the river.

74
00:10:08,427 --> 00:10:11,017
每天早上起來
It wakes me up in the morning.

75
00:10:13,897 --> 00:10:16,517
讓人心曠神怡
Gives me a bath.

76
00:10:16,897 --> 00:10:18,817
還有我的小屋
Does the laundry.

77
00:10:21,397 --> 00:10:25,197
還有我的晚餐 晚上睡覺也特別安靜
Gives me my dinner.  Puts me to sleep real gentle.

78
00:10:26,327 --> 00:10:28,327
還有樹林
I got my river.

79
00:10:29,117 --> 00:10:30,827
還有布蘭迪
I got Brandy.

80
00:10:32,997 --> 00:10:34,917
一切都有了
Paul.

81
00:10:37,707 --> 00:10:40,207
你有什麼呢？
What have you got up here?

82
00:10:41,417 --> 00:10:44,717
我有蘇格蘭威士忌，杜松子酒，奔農酒，還有哈奇拉酒
I got scotch, gin, bourbon, and tequila.

83
00:10:45,297 --> 00:10:47,807
- 這些足夠了吧？ - 很好
- What's it to you, anyhow?  - OK.

84
00:10:49,217 --> 00:10:51,517
好了，夥計，再見
OK, buddy. I'll see you.

85
00:10:52,307 --> 00:10:54,307
跟上，布蘭迪
Come on.

86
00:10:54,937 --> 00:10:56,897
悠著點，布蘭迪
Take it easy, Brandy.

87
00:11:27,637 --> 00:11:28,507
哇！
Ow!

88
00:11:40,727 --> 00:11:41,897
嗯
Hm.

89
00:11:57,827 --> 00:11:59,707
門開著
It's open.

90
00:12:02,627 --> 00:12:04,507
你是保羅 格羅根嗎？
Paul Grogan?

91
00:12:05,927 --> 00:12:09,637
你好，我叫瑪吉.邁克歐文 是為一家找人公司工作的
Hi. I'm Maggie McKeown.  I work for a skip-tracing company.

92
00:12:09,927 --> 00:12:12,807
- 什麼公司？ - 我們查找失蹤人口
- What's that?  - We find missing people.

93
00:12:13,307 --> 00:12:15,727
是我前妻叫你來的嗎？
Did my ex-wife send you?

94
00:12:16,017 --> 00:12:17,727
不
No.

95
00:12:17,937 --> 00:12:19,307
嗯
Um...

96
00:12:19,517 --> 00:12:22,317
我找兩個年輕人
I'm looking for a pair of teenage kids.

97
00:12:22,607 --> 00:12:25,237
他們的朋友說他們可能來這兒旅行了
Some friends said they might  be backpacking up here.

98
00:12:25,397 --> 00:12:29,027
我沒看見他們，你找別人去問吧
I haven't seen 'em. Did you  talk to the sheriff's people?

99
00:12:29,317 --> 00:12:32,197
- 他們說這是一座大山 - 對，確實如此
- They said it was a big mountain.  - They're right. It is.

100
00:12:34,537 --> 00:12:38,917
我猜他們是沿著河走的，這附近有游泳的地方嗎？
I figured they may have followed the river.  Are there any places to swim near here?

101
00:12:39,417 --> 00:12:42,997
如果他們被淹死了，肯定被衝到大壩去了
Well, if they'd drowned,  they'd be swept down to the dam.

102
00:12:43,337 --> 00:12:45,917
你找錯地方了
So you're startin' at the wrong end.

103
00:12:46,417 --> 00:12:49,007
可能只是找錯人了吧
Boy, you're the wrong end all right.

104
00:12:50,297 --> 00:12:53,927
我是不是打攪你了？ 但我這是很重要的事情
Look, am I interrupting something?  This is kind of important.

105
00:12:54,307 --> 00:12:56,017
嘿
Hey,

106
00:12:56,227 --> 00:12:58,437
你說話口氣不太對，女士
you cool your jets, lady.

107
00:12:58,727 --> 00:13:03,317
我沒有殺人，我幫不了你，因為我沒見過他們
I didn't axe-murder your young couple.  I can't help you. I haven't seen 'em.

108
00:13:06,317 --> 00:13:08,697
這兒附近有什麼棚屋嗎？
Are there any other shacks up here?

109
00:13:09,027 --> 00:13:11,527
只有茅屋，這就是個茅屋
Cabins. This is a cabin.

110
00:13:11,697 --> 00:13:15,827
還有沒有別的？他們可能被綁架在哪兒了？
Are there any more of them? Any places  where they might be holed up?

111
00:13:17,407 --> 00:13:21,417
一個叫傑克的老傢伙在河邊有一個小木屋
There's an old fella named Jack,  has a place down the river a bit,

112
00:13:21,627 --> 00:13:23,837
不過也沒聽說有什麼年輕人來過
but he's not with them.

113
00:13:24,127 --> 00:13:28,007
不過在山頂上有個軍方實驗室
And there was some kind of army  test site way up the mountain.

114
00:13:28,297 --> 00:13:31,637
- 只是已經關閉五六年了 - 那好，我們走吧
- That closed down five or six years ago.  - Come on. Let's go.

115
00:13:31,927 --> 00:13:34,507
- 去哪兒？ - 你帶我去你說的地方
- Go where?  - You're taking me up there.

116
00:13:36,217 --> 00:13:37,807
我不去
Oh, no, I'm not.

117
00:13:42,897 --> 00:13:45,107
你覺得我是在浪費我的時間嗎？
You think I'm wasting my time, don't you?

118
00:13:45,317 --> 00:13:47,897
才不是，你是在浪費我的時間
No. I think you're wastin' my time.

119
00:14:18,517 --> 00:14:22,517
- 發現什麼了嗎？ - 還沒有，不過現在天還早
- Find anything yet?  - Not yet, but it's still early in the day.

120
00:15:03,097 --> 00:15:04,597
大衛！
David!

121
00:15:05,807 --> 00:15:07,317
芭芭拉！
Barbara!

122
00:15:20,537 --> 00:15:23,117
- 軍方在這裡做什麼試驗？ - 天知道
- What were they testing here?  - Who knows?

123
00:15:23,917 --> 00:15:27,417
我和前妻曾來過一次
I hiked up here once with my ex-wife.  They had guard dogs out.

124
00:15:27,837 --> 00:15:30,297
那時籬笆都裝上了電網
The fence was electrified. The works.

125
00:15:38,507 --> 00:15:40,717
BR. 芭芭拉.蘭多夫
"BR." Barbara Randolph.

126
00:15:42,427 --> 00:15:44,307
嗯
Hm.

127
00:15:49,397 --> 00:15:51,027
水好冷
Man, that is cold.

128
00:15:51,227 --> 00:15:53,737
他們的父母說他們的水性都不錯
Their parents said they  were excellent swimmers.

129
00:15:54,027 --> 00:15:56,697
他們不會現在才浮起來吧？
Wouldn't they be floatin'  up on top by now?

130
00:15:56,907 --> 00:15:59,407
屍體浮上來需要一段時間
It takes a while for  the body to bloat with gas.

131
00:15:59,697 --> 00:16:01,697
你還挺專業的
Nice business you're in.

132
00:16:02,037 --> 00:16:04,327
這池塘有沒有放水塞子呢？
You think there's a way  to pull the plug on this?

133
00:16:12,207 --> 00:16:15,797
- 熱帶魚？ - 看上去像是實驗用的
- Tropical fish?  - Looks like it's for laboratory rats.

134
00:16:16,127 --> 00:16:20,007
訓練他們穿越障礙找到食物
You know, where they had to get through  an obstacle course to get a reward.

135
00:16:20,307 --> 00:16:21,307
嗯
Hm.

136
00:16:31,017 --> 00:16:33,027
還是熱的
Still warm.

137
00:17:29,417 --> 00:17:31,917
過來，快看這個
Come here. Take a look at this.

138
00:17:36,297 --> 00:17:37,627
噁心
Yeuch.

139
00:17:44,807 --> 00:17:48,727
我們走吧，這地方讓我毛骨悚然
Let's get outta here.  This place gives me the creeps.

140
00:18:04,407 --> 00:18:06,697
嘿！你幹什麼…
Hey! What are you...

141
00:18:10,707 --> 00:18:13,327
他們來過這兒，沒錯
Well, they've been here all right.

142
00:18:15,417 --> 00:18:17,797
而且沒有離開
And they never left.

143
00:18:20,427 --> 00:18:24,137
- 我要把池塘的水全部放掉 - 可是沒有人允許
- I say we drain the pond.  - Well, now. Now, wait a minute.

144
00:18:24,427 --> 00:18:28,517
你是不能這樣做的
You can't do that without gettin'  somebody's permission, you know.

145
00:18:30,597 --> 00:18:33,727
這是我們解決問題最快的辦法
If it works it's the quickest way  to know if they're down there.

146
00:18:33,897 --> 00:18:36,317
天吶，你在幹什麼？
What are you doing?

147
00:19:08,927 --> 00:19:11,227
你沒事吧？
Are you all right?

148
00:19:16,607 --> 00:19:18,517
- 他還活著嗎 - 他還有氣
- He's breathing.  - No thanks to you.

149
00:19:18,817 --> 00:19:22,817
- 都怪你，該怎麼辦，我有任務在身 - 反正我又不會怪你
- What was I supposed to do?  - I would have got loose in a second.

150
00:19:23,237 --> 00:19:27,407
- 我的酒壺都被你打壞了 - 能讓我喝口水嗎？
- Look at this. You put a dent in it.  - Could I have a sip of that, please?

151
00:19:28,827 --> 00:19:30,827
那不是水
It's not water.

152
00:19:41,007 --> 00:19:43,717
- 怎麼樣？ - 有點鹹
- What is it?  - The water's salty.

153
00:19:48,007 --> 00:19:49,427
這個池塘的水會放到哪兒去？
Where does this drain to?

154
00:19:49,507 --> 00:19:51,927
軍方接管之前，這個池塘是孵化魚苗用的
It was a fish hatchery  before the army took it over.

155
00:19:52,227 --> 00:19:55,097
也許是放到河裡去了
It probably drains  underground into the river.

156
00:19:55,937 --> 00:19:57,107
啊噢
Uh-oh.

157
00:20:04,027 --> 00:20:09,527
可能是條狗，可它怎麼會掉到這兒來
I think it's a dog. I don't suppose  they would have fit through here.

158
00:20:10,027 --> 00:20:12,327
一點肉也不剩
Not in one piece.

159
00:20:14,207 --> 00:20:16,417
你覺得剛才那個人還在那兒嗎？
You think he's all right up there?

160
00:20:19,417 --> 00:20:21,127
哦，糟糕
Oh, shit.

161
00:20:24,627 --> 00:20:26,217
我的天啊
Oh, my God.

162
00:20:37,727 --> 00:20:40,607
我肯定是忘了拔鑰匙
I guess I must have left  the keys in it. Huh?

163
00:21:20,097 --> 00:21:22,517
- 他還活著 - 他真命大
- He's alive.  - He's indestructible.

164
00:21:25,317 --> 00:21:27,817
別怕，別怕，沒事
Easy. Easy, now. Easy. Easy.

165
00:21:29,027 --> 00:21:31,817
- 你闖禍了 - 我闖了什麼禍？
- Razorteeth.  - What's "razorteeth"?

166
00:21:32,027 --> 00:21:33,617
- 你把池塘的水放了？ - 是的…
- You drained the pond?  - Yes...

167
