爸爸，你經常這樣抓魚嗎？我說在你小時候
I thought you knew all about this kind  of fishing, from when you were a boy.

323
00:33:53,517 --> 00:33:57,317
我小時候抓魚沒這麼費勁
Listen, when I was a boy we made  our own nets and made 'em right.

324
00:33:58,107 --> 00:34:01,697
越纏越緊了，哇！
Jesus. It feels like  something's snagged in here. Ow!

325
00:34:02,327 --> 00:34:04,407
- 被咬了嗎？ - 啊！
- Did you get bit?  - Ouch!

326
00:34:04,697 --> 00:34:06,827
- 啊！ - 爸爸！
- Ow!  - Dad!

327
00:34:06,997 --> 00:34:10,207
- 呆在那裡！別過來！ - 爸爸！爸爸！
- Stay back! Stay back!  - Dad! Dad!

328
00:34:20,797 --> 00:34:21,927
爸爸！
Dad!

329
00:34:25,517 --> 00:34:28,017
- 政府付你工資嗎？ - 當然付
- The government paid you?  - Of course they paid.

330
00:34:28,427 --> 00:34:31,727
細菌戰武器，炸彈，化學武器
Where there's germ warfare,  the bomb, chemical warfare,

331
00:34:32,607 --> 00:34:35,317
這些都是需要很多錢的，我們是特殊機構
there's plenty of money.  Special agencies.

332
00:34:36,897 --> 00:34:41,197
他們付的錢比我私下做研究賺到的錢多得多
They pay. They pay a lot better  than they do in private research.

333
00:34:42,117 --> 00:34:43,907
就為了養幾條魚
For raisin' fish.

334
00:34:45,027 --> 00:34:47,617
不，是遺傳學
Oh, no. It's a matter of genetics.

335
00:34:49,207 --> 00:34:51,707
用放射性物質進行有選擇的繁殖
Radiation. Selective breeding.

336
00:34:52,627 --> 00:34:55,707
他們把這種研究叫軍用遺傳學
They called it Operation Razorteeth.

337
00:34:58,127 --> 00:35:00,007
那些是幹什麼用的？
What was it all for?

338
00:35:00,297 --> 00:35:03,717
破壞敵人的用水系統
To destroy the river systems  of the North Vietnamese.

339
00:35:04,007 --> 00:35:09,097
我們的目標是繁育出可以在冷水中生存的食人魚
Our goal was to develop a strain of this  killer fish that could survive in cold water

340
00:35:09,427 --> 00:35:11,727
並且能以最快的速度進行繁殖
and then breed at an accelerated rate.

341
00:35:12,807 --> 00:35:15,397
可惜沒能投入應用
We had everything. Blank cheque.

342
00:35:15,897 --> 00:35:18,527
因為戰爭結束了
And then the war ended.

343
00:35:19,027 --> 00:35:20,897
聽你這麼說好像很失望
You sound disappointed.

344
00:35:21,527 --> 00:35:23,617
之後他們在池塘裡放了毒藥
They poisoned the water.

345
00:35:23,907 --> 00:35:28,037
準備把它們都殺死
After all that work,  they poisoned the water.

346
00:35:28,697 --> 00:35:30,707
可是還是有些魚活了下來
But some survived.

347
00:35:30,907 --> 00:35:34,997
我們研究出的變異品種可以抵抗毒藥
We developed a lot of mutants and a few  of them were able to resist the poison.

348
00:35:35,417 --> 00:35:38,207
這些變異品種繁殖能力變得越來越強
They ate their own. Their own dead.

349
00:35:38,417 --> 00:35:43,127
就像是一個新的物種
And then began to breed  like some wild species.

350
00:35:44,137 --> 00:35:47,007
突然之間就有了好幾百條 甚至是幾千條
Suddenly there were hundreds.  Maybe thousands.

351
00:35:47,717 --> 00:35:52,017
- 你的實驗還是很成功的嘛，嗯？ - 這本來是為軍事防衛而設的科學研究
- Our tax dollars at work, huh?  - That's science in the service of defence.

352
00:35:52,437 --> 00:35:56,227
當然現在已經不是了
Sure. Spreadin' strains  of bacteria in the subway system.

353
00:35:56,607 --> 00:36:00,817
它們在河中是會吃人的
You put them in the river where they  could kill people. lncluding civilians.

354
00:36:01,317 --> 00:36:04,407
- 包括平民，以及在河裡游泳的小孩 - 我可沒有殺人
- And kids swimming in the rivers.  - I never killed anybody.

355
00:36:04,697 --> 00:36:08,407
如果有人想殺人那是政府和軍方
If you wanna talk about killing,  talk to your politicians, the military.

356
00:36:08,697 --> 00:36:10,827
不，我是個科學家
No, no. I'm a scientist.

357
00:36:11,537 --> 00:36:14,117
- 河裡的小孩 - 什麼？
- Kids in the water.  - What?

358
00:36:14,917 --> 00:36:16,207
大壩
The dam.

359
00:36:16,417 --> 00:36:20,297
他們每隔幾天就開閘放水一次 以保持湖裡穩定的水量
They let water through every few days  to keep the level steady on the new lake.

360
00:36:20,627 --> 00:36:25,127
大壩下面有度假村和夏令營，小孩們都在那兒，快點
The resort's down there. Summer camp.  All those kids. Come on.

361
00:36:49,407 --> 00:36:51,407
Hey, stop splashin'！
Hey, stop splashin'!

362
00:36:53,617 --> 00:36:57,497
這純粹是個科學研究 可一旦暫時沒有戰爭
It was pure research.  No scrounging for grant money.

363
00:36:57,917 --> 00:37:01,207
這些政客就把資金撤走了 你知道這對於一個科學家的意義
No academic politics. You don't know  what that means to a scientist.

364
00:37:02,417 --> 00:37:05,007
你餵養了它們，你讓它們變異而存活下來
You fed them. You kept them alive.

365
00:37:06,007 --> 00:37:08,217
我私下裡繼續做實驗
I continued the experiment.

366
00:37:08,507 --> 00:37:11,217
對於這個物種我還有很多工作要做
There was so much more  I could do with the species.

367
00:37:11,597 --> 00:37:14,097
它們會變得更有用
So much further I could take them.

368
00:37:15,097 --> 00:37:18,017
你們不會認為我要負全部責任吧？
You're not holding me responsible?

369
00:37:20,227 --> 00:37:25,107
我認為是的  池塘的塞子是你拔掉的 難道要我負全部責任嗎？
I think you are. You pulled the plug and  you're holding me responsible. lncredible.

370
00:37:26,527 --> 00:37:28,197
居然怪到我頭上來了
You're blaming me.

371
00:37:29,117 --> 00:37:32,197
你如果再不閉嘴 我就把這個桿子塞進去
I think if you open your mouth again  I'll stick this pole in it.

372
00:37:32,407 --> 00:37:36,917
- 他們是不是已經把大壩的閘門打開了？ - 我不知道，只希望還沒有
- You think they've opened the dam yet?  - I don't know. We can only hope not.

373
00:37:37,917 --> 00:37:39,917
爸爸
Daddy.

374
00:37:45,207 --> 00:37:47,797
快點
Let's move it.

375
00:37:48,127 --> 00:37:51,007
- 那船在下沉 - 對
- It's sinking, Paul. The canoe is sinking.  - Yeah.

376
00:37:57,517 --> 00:37:59,517
爸爸？
Daddy?

377
00:38:02,607 --> 00:38:05,027
爸爸！爸爸！你在哪兒
Daddy! Daddy! It's going under.

378
00:38:06,527 --> 00:38:09,407
別下水
Don't do it! Get outta there!

379
00:38:13,117 --> 00:38:15,117
快點，瑪吉
Come on, Maggie.

380
00:38:59,707 --> 00:39:01,207
堅持住！堅持
Hold it here. Hold it.

381
00:39:10,507 --> 00:39:13,007
快點！快點！
Come on! Come on! Come here!

382
00:39:15,007 --> 00:39:17,717
快點！抓住我的手
Come on! Give me your hand.

383
00:39:18,017 --> 00:39:20,307
快上船，快把他拉上來
Get the doctor. OK, now the doctor.

384
00:39:43,117 --> 00:39:44,997
放鬆，教授
Easy, Doc.

385
00:39:45,627 --> 00:39:47,917
你不會死的
Here. Here you go.

386
00:39:50,917 --> 00:39:55,137
我們該怎麼辦？該怎麼辦？
What do we do? What do we do?  How do we stop them?

387
00:40:03,017 --> 00:40:04,437
哦，天吶
Oh, Christ.

388
00:40:13,027 --> 00:40:15,407
營員們，該上來吃飯了
Campers. No swinging after lunch.

389
00:40:42,017 --> 00:40:44,807
現在可以確認它們能在冷水中生存了
So far we know that they  can live in cold water.

390
00:40:47,517 --> 00:40:50,107
它們好像是順流而下
They seem to be  moving downstream.

391
00:40:50,607 --> 00:40:54,317
我們必須找到能夠對付它們的人
Gotta find someone who knows  how to deal with these things.

392
00:40:55,407 --> 00:40:58,317
我們得先到大壩到那兒去打電話
There'll be a phone at the dam.  We can call on ahead.

393
00:41:01,907 --> 00:41:04,327
- 嘿 - 怎麼了？
- Hey.  - What?

394
00:41:05,997 --> 00:41:10,497
我不知道是怎麼回事，好像下面有東西在動
I don't know. It seems like  the lashing's workin' loose.

395
00:41:17,717 --> 00:41:21,007
保羅... 下面有東西
Paul... there's something under us.

396
00:41:34,027 --> 00:41:37,027
是血！是血把它們引來的
His blood. It's the doc's blood.

397
00:41:38,317 --> 00:41:42,197
它們在拆船，一點點的咬斷繩子
It's seepin' through. They're eatin'  away at the lashing to get to it.

398
00:41:45,197 --> 00:41:47,827
- 爸爸！ - 不要，我們必須減輕負載
- Daddy!  - Let go, son. No. We gotta get rid of him.

399
00:41:48,117 --> 00:41:50,497
不，我爸爸掉進河裡去了
No. That's what happened to my daddy.

400
00:41:50,707 --> 00:41:52,997
- 快點 - 它們在吃他
- Let go.  - They're eating him.

401
00:41:53,417 --> 00:41:55,627
他們吃掉了他！
They're eating him!

402
00:41:58,927 --> 00:42:01,717
- 過來 - 它們吃了我爸爸！
- Come here.  - They got my daddy!

403
00:42:57,527 --> 00:42:59,817
你沒事吧，孩子？你怎麼樣？
You OK, boy? How about you?

404
00:43:00,027 --> 00:43:03,027
- 我沒事 - 你們待在這兒
- I'm all right.  - You gotta stay here.

405
00:43:03,407 --> 00:43:07,407
我到大壩去，要趕在他們開閘放水之前
I'm gonna try to get to the dam before  they let 'em through with the water.

406
00:43:20,467 --> 00:43:23,967
警告：喇叭聲後隨即開閘放水

407
00:43:49,827 --> 00:43:53,627
Acres and acres of reclaimed land nestled in a scenic mountain valley,

408
00:43:53,997 --> 00:43:56,337
site of the newly formed Lost River Lake.

409
00:43:58,207 --> 00:44:01,417
Swimming, sailing, snorkeling, skin diving, shuffleboard,

410
00:44:01,797 --> 00:44:05,007
and Buck Gardner's Aquarena Amusement Arcade.

411
00:44:07,927 --> 00:44:11,597
So pack up your RVs, your station Wagons, your trailers and cars,

412
00:44:11,937 --> 00:44:16,227
and hustle on up to Lost River Campsite for a free introductory Weekend.

413
00:44:24,817 --> 00:44:28,527
別開閘！ 你說什麼？別開閘！
Don't open it!  Whatever you do, don't open it.

414
00:45:00,317 --> 00:45:04,027
好了，下車集中，快點！
All right, men, off your butts.  Fall in. Move it!

415
00:45:13,327 --> 00:45:17,207
我們對此心存疑慮，因為我們不能每天都能碰到這種事
Forgive our scepticism, but we don't  come across stories like yours every day.

416
00:45:17,627 --> 00:45:20,417
食人魚是熱帶魚種，這裡又不是亞馬遜河
Piranha are warm-water fish.  This is hardly the Amazon.

417
00:45:20,627 --> 00:45:25,127
我告訴你了，這是變異品種 它們已經殺了五個人了
But I told you, these are mutations.  They've already killed five people.

418
00:45:25,427 --> 00:45:28,717
- 是科幻小說吧 - 誘餌準備好了嗎？
- Science fiction.  - You ready with that bait, soldier?

419
00:45:29,007 --> 00:45:31,507
- 是的，長官 - 放吧
- Yes, sir.  - Let her go, son.

420
00:45:38,307 --> 00:45:42,897
據我所知，軍方在山頂確實有個實驗室 不過那在72年就關閉了
Actually, a piranha was caught once  in a pond in Miami, in '72, I believe.

421
00:45:43,227 --> 00:45:46,607
他們已經都把魚毒死了 不會還有什麼食人魚跑到河裡來
But the Fish and Game Commission  poisoned the water, and that was that.

422
00:45:47,027 --> 00:45:50,407
- 這我們都知道 - 有時候會有一些謠言，但…
- That was that, huh?  - The rumours persisted, you know, but...

423
00:45:50,617 --> 00:45:53,037
拉起來
Pull it in, son.

424
00:46:01,997 --> 00:46:04,507
軍事，讓少校準備炸藥
Sergeant, tell the major  to start the pumps.

425
00:46:04,707 --> 00:46:07,297
我們要把它們封鎖在這個河區
We should be able to  contain them in this area.

426
00:46:07,507 --> 00:46:11,637
把河邊的度假村和夏令營都關閉 我們可能會用新型劇毒藥品
Piranha travel in schools, and we've  brought heavy doses of rotenone 235.

427
00:46:12,007 --> 00:46:15,017
- 你確信這些魚能被毒死嗎？ - 這一帶的河水會不會受污染呢？
- Came well-prepared, didn't you?  - Won't it ruin the river?

428
00:46:15,307 --> 00:46:17,437
有的時候僅僅是污染還不夠，還得摧毀
Sometimes you need to destroy  in order to save.

429
00:46:17,727 --> 00:46:20,607
如果它們知道了我們的計劃之後又逆河而上呢？
What if they realise they're  bein' slaughtered and leave?

430
00:46:20,897 --> 00:46:23,107
格羅根先生，我們對付的是魚
We're talking about fish, Mr Grogan.

431
00:46:23,317 --> 00:46:27,027
- 它們不會知道太多的東西 - 等一等，你以為自己在哄小孩嗎？
- They don't realise much of anything.  - Who are you trying to kid?

432
00:46:27,317 --> 00:46:30,107
如果你不知道它們的厲害怎麼會帶這麼多人過來呢？
You must've known  all along they were here.

433
00:46:30,407 --> 00:46:35,117
行了，格羅根先生 現在只有你和這位女士知道它們存在
OK. You and Miss McKeown are the only  two civilians who know about this project.

434
00:46:35,830 --> 00:46:41,002
上校的意思是說 他希望你們能加入我們的隊伍
What the colonel means is that he'd like  you to join us. Become one of our team.

435
00:46:43,630 --> 00:46:45,507
我明白了
It figures.

436
00:46:54,724 --> 00:46:55,934
不可能
Impossible.

437
00:46:57,018 --> 00:47:01,606
你是個上校，對嗎？我肯定你能看懂地圖
Look, you're a full colonel, right?  I assume you can read a map. Here.

438
00:47:02,232 --> 00:47:04,234
我們在大壩，對吧？
We are here at the dam, OK?

439
00:47:04,401 --> 00:47:07,737
再看這兒，這條小溪流入大壩
Over here you'll see there's  a stream that feeds into it.

440
00:47:08,113 --> 00:47:12,409
好，從這條小溪逆流而上大概8公里路 你看這兒有個分岔
Follow the stream back for an eighth  of a mile and you see there's a fork.

441
00:47:12,701 --> 00:47:15,203
從這個小支流，一直向下
Take this branch, follow it downstream,

442
00:47:15,412 --> 00:47:19,124
你會發現水流可以通向大壩的另一頭
and you'll see it empties into the  river on the other side of the dam.

443
00:47:19,416 --> 00:47:22,711
換句話說，這些魚知道怎麼跨越障礙
In other words, the piranha have  a way to get around the obstacle.

444
00:47:22,919 --> 00:47:26,715
如果他是對的，你不覺得應該採取點行動嗎？
Even if there's a chance he's right,  don't you think you should do something?

445
00:47:27,132 --> 00:47:32,220
不，即使支流存在，食人魚也沒有這個耐力和智力
No. lf a bypass exists, piranha haven't  the intelligence or the motivation to find it.

446
00:47:32,512 --> 00:47:37,434
可你沒有聽到浩克說的話，他培養了它們的耐力和智力
But you know Hoak was breeding them  for endurance and intelligence and...

447
00:47:38,018 --> 00:47:41,313
鮑伯是個夢想家
- Well, Bob was a dreamer. He, er...  - Bob?

448
00:47:43,437 --> 00:47:45,317
鮑伯？
Dr Hoak?

449
00:47:45,397 --> 00:47:47,317
你認識他？
You knew him?

450
00:47:48,527 --> 00:47:51,527
魚類研究是一個很小的領域
Fish genetics is a very small field.

451
00:47:51,737 --> 00:47:54,407
你們是朋友嗎？
You were friends?

452
00:47:55,827 --> 00:47:59,537
我們比朋友的關係更密切些
Let's say we were  a great deal more than that.

453
00:48:01,327 --> 00:48:03,497
你在為他隱瞞真相
You're covering up.

454
00:48:06,127 --> 00:48:10,297
你是華克斯曼嗎？你是不是擔心軍隊會除掉你
Is it Waxman? Are you afraid of what  the army might do to you if you...

455
00:48:10,717 --> 00:48:15,007
不是怕，我是科學家，我是我們部門的領導
No, I'm not afraid. I'm a scientist.  I'm head of my department.

456
00:48:15,297 --> 00:48:18,507
是個很重要的部門
It's just that there are priorities, and...

457
00:48:20,217 --> 00:48:23,017
有的東西比幾條人命更重要
some things are more important  than a few lives.

458
00:48:23,597 --> 00:48:27,227
浩克教授可不這麼想
That's not how Dr Hoak felt.  Not at the end.

459
00:48:28,897 --> 00:48:31,607
至少他在生命的最後一刻不是
As I said, he was a dreamer.

460
00:48:33,027 --> 00:48:36,527
- 我剛才說過，他是個夢想家 - 嘿，等等
- The situation is under control.  - Hold on. What is this?

461
00:48:36,817 --> 00:48:39,037
為何你不聽我說呢？
Why won't you listen to me?

462
00:48:39,197 --> 00:48:42,117
你能不能出去一下？
Would you excuse us  for a moment, please?

463
00:48:43,327 --> 00:48:46,707
對於你來說，格羅根先生，這個實驗項目不存在
As far as you're concerned,  this project does not exist.

464
00:48:46,997 --> 00:48:49,417
食人魚不存在，知道嗎？
The piranha do not exist.

465
00:48:49,627 --> 00:48:51,707
- 如果我抗議呢？ - 保羅...
Paul...  - And if I make a squawk?  - Paul...

466
00:48:51,917 --> 00:48:55,127
國家安全部門會被迫採取極端的措施
The interests of national security  permit extreme measures.

467
00:48:55,297 --> 00:48:57,927
得了吧，戰爭已經結束了
Oh, come on! The war's over, dammit!

468
00:48:58,217 --> 00:49:00,717
格羅根先生，還會有別的戰爭
There'll be other wars, Mr Grogan.

