See you in the mornin'.

529
00:53:39,837 --> 00:53:44,297
今晚你們得在這兒過夜了，你們好好待著吧
Well, you best make yourself comfortable,  folks. You'll be spending the night.

530
00:53:44,627 --> 00:53:48,297
- 可以打電話嗎？ - 這裡可不行
- What about a phone call?  - I don't wanna hear it.

531
00:53:48,507 --> 00:53:50,427
我不能再讓你們惹出什麼亂子
I don't wanna hear it.

532
00:53:50,717 --> 00:53:53,017
你們還是老老實實呆著
I gotta get back on that road now.

533
00:53:53,307 --> 00:53:56,597
再見了，夥計們，明早見
So you folks, you just behave yourselves.

534
00:53:56,937 --> 00:53:59,727
