Uh-huh. I really appreciate the warning.  I'll brief my staff. We'll take care of it.

548
00:54:58,207 --> 00:55:00,117
是的，您不用擔心
Yeah. Don't worry.

549
00:55:01,497 --> 00:55:04,917
隨便說一句，明天您過來吧
Uh-huh. By the way,  are you comin' down tomorrow?

550
00:55:05,707 --> 00:55:09,507
很好，很好，您的光臨會給慶典增添光彩
Ah, good. Your presence will lend  a certain prestige to the opening.

551
00:55:09,927 --> 00:55:11,137
Mm-hm.

552
00:55:11,217 --> 00:55:12,637
