No. No, Colonel.  Nobody knows about your investment.

554
00:55:20,937 --> 00:55:23,397
只有另外幾個秘密的合夥投資人
With me, a silent partner's  privacy is sacred.

555
00:55:23,607 --> 00:55:27,107
他們不參與管理，我向您發誓沒人知道
I swear to you on my honour  as a Texan, nobody knows.

556
00:55:28,897 --> 00:55:30,407
是的，將軍
Yes, Colonel.

557
00:55:30,607 --> 00:55:33,027
