- What's the matter?  - I don't know.

571
00:56:32,627 --> 00:56:35,007
有些事情…有些事情不太對勁
Something... Something's wrong.

572
00:56:36,507 --> 00:56:39,307
來吧，和我一塊兒下水吧，對身體有好處的
Come on, come with me.  It'll do you some good.

573
00:56:39,517 --> 00:56:42,307
- 也許你是對的 - 行了，我們下水吧
- You're probably right.  - Good. OK.

574
00:56:43,517 --> 00:56:45,397
格羅根夫人，你們在幹什麼！
Grogan, turn off that flashlight!

575
00:56:46,107 --> 00:56:48,107
別害怕，就我一個人
Don't be alarmed - it's only me.

576
00:56:48,607 --> 00:56:51,817
有謠言說夏令營裡有人半夜三更到這兒來游泳
There's a rumour some campers  are coming for a midnight swim.

577
00:56:52,237 --> 00:56:55,907
如果被我抓住的話她們就慘了
If I catch them swimming, they'll be  in pretty hot water, I can tell you.

578
00:56:56,197 --> 00:56:58,827
