Being a plumber,  he used what he knew best.

594
00:58:16,607 --> 00:58:18,817
怎麼回事？
What the hell was that?

595
00:58:19,617 --> 00:58:22,407
你在幹什麼？你沒事吧？
What are you doing? Are you all right?

596
