No. But he came pretty  close a couple of times.

599
00:58:35,007 --> 00:58:37,717
只要看門的人會進來
Pretty damn close.

600
00:58:40,927 --> 00:58:46,097
怎麼回事？聽起來像是天花板掉了 滿地的水是怎麼回事？
What's all that racket? Sounds like the  roof fell in. What's all this water from?

